\"Pidcock's race was in danger of unravelling when he suffered a flat front tyre on the fourth of eight laps, shortly after he had taken control of the 35km race with an attack which split the pack.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock's race\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"a flat front tyre\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth of eight laps\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the 35km race\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"an attack\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"the pack\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having fallen 40 seconds behind French hope Victor Koretzky, Pidcock fought his way back to reclaim the lead with a lap and a half to go, but the pair traded blows in the last couple of kilometres - dramatically touching wheels - before Pidcock burst forward to take the win.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.48093962600007856, \"rank\": 0.6837114205462054, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\", \"score\": 0.9999880939516794, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Victor Koretzky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"a lap\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"a half\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"kilometres - dramatically touching wheels\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock was booed by the home crowds at Elancourt Hill, who had been ecstatic when Koretzky had attacked on the final climb of the race - the sort of territory where Pidcock would be expected to make a move - to take the lead late on.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elancourt\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"the home crowds\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"Koretzky\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the final climb\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the sort\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"territory\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But their hearts would be broken after Pidcock got his nose in front of Koretzky as the path narrowed before a tree, the decisive moment in a tense race.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their hearts\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"his nose\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from