this race\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"his determination\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the final two laps\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"a pulsating contest\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock revealed how his racing instincts had got him over the line for gold.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"his racing instincts\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2314}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was all going pretty well and I knew that Victor would be strong and then the puncture happened.\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"score\": 0.9990346719695423, \"rank\": 0.0009643477194856848, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the puncture\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were not ready in the pits but he did a fast change and I knew at that point that I had five laps and thought anything was possible.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pits\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast change\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"five laps\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Suddenly I was coming really fast back to Victor but I could not get rid of him and I knew how fast he was on the last lap.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2633, \"end\": 2639, \"title\": \"http:/